The standard menu allows navigation through five pre-installed programs.
<ul>
<li>Use the A and B buttons to scroll through the five programs.</li>
<li>Shake to confirm the selected program.</li>
<li>Press the two buttons A and B <b>simultaneously </b> to enter the menu.</li>
